RasterFunctionTemplate.Name: Scaled Coherence
RasterFunctionTemplate.Description: Apply a min-max stretch to the coherence products, which are scaled to range from 0 to 100.

Function.Name: Stretch
Function.Description: Applies a min-max stretch to the coherence dataset that matches the scaled values of the source rasters, which range from 0 to 100. The original median coherence values are multiplied by 100 to output values in 8-bit unsigned integer format.
